Class JdbcMaintenanceRecordService

java.lang.Object
com.gcu.agms.service.impl.JdbcMaintenanceRecordService
All Implemented Interfaces:
MaintenanceRecordService
@Service("jdbcMaintenanceRecordService") @Primary public class JdbcMaintenanceRecordService extends Object implements MaintenanceRecordService
JDBC implementation of the MaintenanceRecordService interface. This service uses a database repository for maintenance record operations.
